There was one other sighting in Yorba Linda on or around January 26th 2008
divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving north bound on the 57 fwy heading towards Yorba Linda when I saw 2 meteorite like objects falling in the NW sky. I also saw what it looked like to be a plane flying around in the same general area. During the event the glowing tails coming from the 2 objects seemed to turned off and then resumed again after a short period of time.
